notes.title: Author Contributions
notes.p: C.-W.L. and S.-L.F. performed the bioassay and analyzed the data and manuscript writing. Y.-C.C. conducted the isolation and structure elucidation of the constituents. C.-Y.H. performed quantification of components and manuscript writing. J.-J.C. planned, designed and organized all of the research of this study and the preparation of the manuscript. All authors read and approved the final version of the manuscript.
